### Generate BASIC PRG - Hello World Loop (JSON-RPC MCP)
POST http://localhost:8080/
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "ultimate_generate_basic_prg",
    "arguments": {
      "basicSource": "10 PRINT \"HELLO WORLD\"\n20 GOTO 10"
    }
  }
}

